metadata.name: $PEPE SOUP (ETH)
metadata.description:
the most memeable soup can in existence. 

Pepe soup is tired of watching everyone play hot soup with the endless derivative ShibaCuGMElonKishuTurboAsFlokiMoon Inu soup cans. The other soups have had their day. It’s time for the most recognizable meme soup in the world to take the reign as king of the meme soup.

Pepe  soup is here to make meme soup great again. Launched stealth $PEPE SOUP is a soup for the people, forever. Fueled by pure memetic power, let Pepe soup show you the way. In Lord Soup we trust.

All jokes aside, there is a $PEPE SOUP path ahead. We dont wan’t to give everything away on day 1, Expect surprises along the way ;)
